text: José Antonio Aguirre may refer to: *José Antonio Aguirre (politician) (1904–1960), Spanish footballer and Basque politician *José Antonio Aguirre (early Californian) (1799–1860), Spanish-born settler in Alta California *José Antonio Aguirre (boxer) (born 1975), Mexican world champion boxer ==See also== *José Aguirre (disambiguation)
